: moving toward the future</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Federica Vernuccio</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Roberto Cannella</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Tommaso Vincenzo Bartolotta</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Massimo Galia</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">An Tang</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Giuseppe Brancatelli</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">7 December 2021 | European Radiology Experimental, Vol. 5, No. 1</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1186/s41747-021-00250-0">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1016/j.mric.2021.05.014"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.mric.2021.05.014">MR Imaging Contrast Agents</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Silvia D. Chang</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Guilherme Moura Cunha</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Victoria Chernyak</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2021Aug1 | Magnetic Resonance Imaging Clinics of North America, Vol. 29, No. 3</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.mric.2021.05.014">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.3390/jcm10163535"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.3390/jcm10163535">Inadequate Ultrasound Examination in Hepatocellular Carcinoma Surveillance: A Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inli